==Install upload-image==

The program uses python distutils, so typical installation procedure is:

    $ wget http://upload-image.googlecode.com/files/upload-image-0.3.tar.gz
    $ tar xzf upload-image-0.3.tar.gz
    $ cd upload-image-0.3
    $ sudo python2.5 setup.py install 

If you are using Debian/Ubuntu please install corresponding deb package:
    
    $ wget http://upload-image.googlecode.com/files/upload-image_0.3-1_all.deb
    $ sudo dpkg -i upload-image_0.3-1_all.deb

==Runtime Requirements==

To run upload-image you need the following python modules:

* pycurl [[http://pycurl.sourceforge.net/]]



